# Linear.app Website Clone

This project is an exact replication of the [Linear.app](https://linear.app) website, including all UI/UX elements, animations, and interactive features.

## Overview

This clone aims to recreate the Linear.app website with pixel-perfect accuracy, including:

- The gradient animated background
- Shimmer effects and animations
- Responsive design
- Interactive elements
- Exact typography and color scheme

## Features Replicated

- **Header & Navigation**: Fixed header with blur effect, navigation links, and sign-up button
- **Hero Section**: Main headline, subtext, call-to-action buttons, and app interface mockup
- **Client Logos**: Showcase of companies using Linear
- **Features Section**: Grid layout of key features with hover effects
- **Roadmap & Cycles Sections**: Visual representations of Linear's product features
- **Call-to-Action Section**: Final conversion section with gradient background
- **Footer**: Multi-column footer with links and social media

## Technical Implementation

This clone is built using:

- HTML5 for structure
- CSS3 for styling, including:
  - CSS Variables for consistent theming
  - CSS Animations for shimmer effects
  - CSS Gradients for background effects
- Vanilla JavaScript for interactive elements and animations

## Running the Project

This is a static website that can be run without any build tools or server-side code. Simply open the `index.html` file in a web browser to view the site.

For the best experience, use a modern browser like Chrome, Firefox, or Edge.

## Project Structure

```
├── index.html          # Main HTML structure
├── styles.css          # All styles and animations
├── script.js           # JavaScript for interactive elements
├── favicon.svg         # Site favicon
└── README.md           # Project documentation
```

## Design Details

### Color Scheme

The site uses Linear's distinctive color palette:

- Background: #000000 (Black)
- Text: #FFFFFF (White)
- Accent Blue: rgba(100, 100, 255, 0.15)
- Accent Red: rgba(255, 100, 100, 0.1)
- UI Elements: Various shades of white with transparency

### Typography

The site uses the Inter font family, with system fonts as fallbacks:

```css
font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Inter', 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
```

